  "detailed_description": "In <strong>ASTROSWARM</strong>, fight as a lone astronaut against an incoming swarm of zombified astronauts. Travel from planet to planet to find the source of this blight!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/2d7507a29db4e023af864ac4d9814b1e.poster.avif?t=1718243203\" width=480 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/2d7507a29db4e023af864ac4d9814b1e.webm?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/2d7507a29db4e023af864ac4d9814b1e.mp4?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build a variety of different turrets to stave on the unrelenting waves of enemies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Protect your module from attackers or face certain death.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/5707f518a49c77ea1036b6451dc2835e.poster.avif?t=1718243203\" width=480 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/5707f518a49c77ea1036b6451dc2835e.webm?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/5707f518a49c77ea1036b6451dc2835e.mp4?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defeat enemies to level up and gain game-changing power-ups and weapons.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find synergies that will boost your power drastically!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/1a6e6b4e77ef54b96eb17f3882e2ca00.poster.avif?t=1718243203\" width=480 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/1a6e6b4e77ef54b96eb17f3882e2ca00.webm?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/1a6e6b4e77ef54b96eb17f3882e2ca00.mp4?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the resources gained from your battles to get permanent upgrades and obtain new weapons, turrets, and more.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock modifiers that drastically change your play style. Use the ones that fit how you want to play!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "In <strong>ASTROSWARM</strong>, fight as a lone astronaut against an incoming swarm of zombified astronauts. Travel from planet to planet to find the source of this blight!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/2d7507a29db4e023af864ac4d9814b1e.poster.avif?t=1718243203\" width=480 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/2d7507a29db4e023af864ac4d9814b1e.webm?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/2d7507a29db4e023af864ac4d9814b1e.mp4?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build a variety of different turrets to stave on the unrelenting waves of enemies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Protect your module from attackers or face certain death.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/5707f518a49c77ea1036b6451dc2835e.poster.avif?t=1718243203\" width=480 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/5707f518a49c77ea1036b6451dc2835e.webm?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664720/extras/5707f518a49c77ea1036b6451dc2835e.mp4?t=1718243203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defeat enemies to level up and gain game-changing power-ups and weapons.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find synergies that will boost your power drastically!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_